#: ../../source/developer_guide/performance_and_debug/service_profiling_guide.md:242
msgid ""
"If you need to customize the profiling points, it is highly recommended "
"to copy a symbol configuration file to your working directory and point "
"to it with the `PROFILING_SYMBOLS_PATH` environment variable."
msgstr ""
"如果需要自定义性能分析点，强烈建议将符号配置文件复制到您的工作目录，并通过 `PROFILING_SYMBOLS_PATH` 环境变量指向它。"

