#: ../../source/developer_guide/performance_and_debug/service_profiling_guide.md:315
msgid "`len(input_ids)`: get the length of parameter `input_ids`."
msgstr "`len(input_ids)`：获取参数 `input_ids` 的长度。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/performance_and_debug/service_profiling_guide.md:316
